{"tid":55666,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本華人：我是中國人，但沒有國籍","createTime":"2016-12-26T14:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T12:11:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"003f37cea2b721e9d95cf92eacb47dfc359fba5b","tid":55666,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:46:13.000Z","msg":"全球有1200萬無國籍的人，他們是不屬於任何國家的狀態，不具有公民身份，最基礎的醫療教育權利均得不到保障。生活在日本的華人學者陳天璽是他們中的一員，&ldquo;人們通常把國籍作為一種理所當然的東西擁有&rdquo;，如何跨越捆綁無國籍者的國境線，一席現場，探討無國籍生存。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fcw8KT7tN8o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFcw8KT7tN8o&d=ud24qvjcCdzPg0KUTqABCwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=c4e6c89e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fcw8KT7tN8o</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/不了解國家帶來的利弊-如何談全球化-專訪-無國籍-作者陳天璽-134900071.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%84%E5%88%A9%E5%BC%8A-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%AB%87%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%8C%96-%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%84%A1%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D-%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E9%99%B3%E5%A4%A9%E7%92%BD-134900071.html&d=ud24qvjcCdzPg0KUTqABCwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=35fbb6ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/不了解國家帶來的利弊-如何談全球化-專訪-無國籍-作者陳天璽-134900071.html</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上係一個想食三家茶禮, 想抱著 &quot;中國人&quot; 身份又響日本賴死唔走既一條麻煩友"},{"pid":"fc6bb0b047c4330e84f2bf1d9ae9de6398a8e66b","tid":55666,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:47:34.000Z","msg":"NHK紀錄片 『無國籍我的祖國在哪裡？』 (日本韓國人)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x7g6_kTe18I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx7g6_kTe18I&d=ud24qvjcCdzPg0KUTqABCwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=fc237b00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x7g6_kTe18I</a>"},{"pid":"909b8ac6c439b3c6ffb2b24f980